{"type": "article", "id": 46026, "title": "Coach 集团改名 Tapestry，以及，Gucci 不再使用动物毛皮 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-10-12T03:42:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 27239, "name": "NMD"}, {"id": 44642, "name": "GOLF"}, {"id": 35090, "name": "Tyler"}, {"id": 334, "name": "优衣库"}, {"id": 1782, "name": "Coach"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/201710121040122K49Fc1LWZQgfviG.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/card/493133\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Coach 集团突然改名，将专注于多品牌发展</strong></a> | 美国轻奢集团 Coach 改名为 Tapestry（挂毯），以体现其作为多品牌轻奢集团的新形态。该名称变更将于 10 月 31 日生效，更名后集团在纽约证券交易所的代码将从“COH”变为“TPR”。目前，Coach 集团除了 Coach 之外还拥有 Stuart Weitzman 和 Kate Spade 两个品牌。消息传出后，Coach 集团股价大跌 2.67% 至每股 38.9 美元，目前市值约为 110 亿美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012110615WjEcl2y6qtXn4SYO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.430556\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/10/11/gucci-fur-free/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Gucci 宣布将不再使用毛皮制品</strong></a> | Gucci 的首席执行官 Marco Bizzarri 透露，品牌将不再使用动物毛皮作为原料。事实上，上个月在米兰时装周上展示的 Gucci 2018 春夏系列中，就已经开始不用动物毛皮了。</p><p><a href=\"http://magazine.promomarketing.com/article/adidas-drops-three-stripe-lawsuit-juicy-couture/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>adidas 与 Juicy Couture 达成和解，不再起诉后者抄袭</strong></a> | 周二，adidas 向美国俄勒冈州联邦法院递交撤诉申请，表示已和 Juicy Couture 达成了和解协议，不再起诉。半年前，adidas 曾起诉 Juicy Couture 的三条白边运动套装涉嫌抄袭。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>美国说唱歌手 Tyler 的牌子<a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/10/11/tyler-the-creator-golf-fw17/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> GOLF</a> 发布了 2017 秋冬系列 lookbook，色调一如既往地丰富。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012110051SHFEZK1zt7Apgsfc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.459854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017101211002320zgVGBjZe9mi57n.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.459854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012110029Gt1gBV6TXOENnl8F.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.459854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710121100311N6okpmED7CHby2L.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.459854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012110041gYzm12sTXAlJZ50N.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.459854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012110045qyFsZb6MmjeQ3YUK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.459854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710121100540fzLDc8VEyXYubwT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.459854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012110057nxr2oqF89BOdAgkp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.459854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012110058uKfhtdPxUj70giL6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.459854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012110305sTHPWtkzhjr5ufJG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.459854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012110316nJNAF2o5KglLb84O.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.459854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012110318vie54HFwglUk9GnT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.459854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012110652UQESmc7OyoX6vIGH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.459854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012110659JbM7QUxXgz6n9eD3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.459854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>为了讽刺流行的“一次性”文化，设计师 <a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/10/11/luxury-jewellery-rubbish/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hollie Paxton</a> 做了一个名为垃圾的珠宝系列。口香糖包装纸、小票等从“垃圾箱”翻出来的东西变成了该系列的主题。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012110627wFQHbSPK7sWE9frR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012110627Njl57V0o29rdwI4E.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012110627SRNwEfjpygnkJIx5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012110627vw1qj3utFCQLHZSg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012110627Nw6jZK1yzq9L5seR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012110627SDfI7lGvqMBCyanR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012110632I102a6NwAnYevPkd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012110637CzcHUqF59VNb7oAp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>优衣库的 U 系列今日正式上架，来看看都有哪些值得一看的单品： </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012110458Xu0437pK8i5LZPeU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.392187\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012110458nDchmS4OEPQaZvtU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.181818\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017101211050338BliLAjZIzFePsy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.181818\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012110502RrU4WjD0omihG71v.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.181818\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012110508hdy2JA8QjsZUtB7w.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.181818\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710121120078aLnEv6iY5zZSApg.png\" data-ratio=\"1.518681\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012112009iUwTy0SFxJ5sq8fA.png\" data-ratio=\"1.509890\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710121120101lGsw7bn6oUg0ODT.png\" data-ratio=\"1.526549\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012112011pgxzt4ilJ5r0KfC1.png\" data-ratio=\"1.508772\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012112012y2aGd7xtoBW3Yrim.png\" data-ratio=\"1.503254\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><p>KITH 与 Off-White 的联名款<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/10/kith-x-off-white-just-global\" rel=\"nofollow\"> JUST GLOBAL </a>正式发布。该系列特意将 OFF 的 O 换成地球标志，包括黑、白、灰三色的长短袖 T 和帽衫的设计，将于 10 月 13 日正式登陆 KITH 实体店。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012110525NoDut28KR7pBaLsU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012110525r3qOGQZteTfBJ7Ma.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498750\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012110525OvLqjxtEfu2kndKc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710121105269yKR3v2OHBAl8PrQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012110526oRkDieQNHy1UfpYm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171012110527TZIJmOYjrg4HUB6k.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-fo